name: LibMix
description:
A mix of Rev Animated, PerfectWorldv2, AOM3, Protogen v2.2 anime, Babes, CamelliaMix_2.5D, dalcefo_painting and My Lora style. Even though I didn't get the result that I wanted to, but I think it's a decent model, so I share it with everyone here. All preview images are t2i + hires.fix without any inpainting. It's kind of a mix of 2.5D and painting models, and have to use hires.fix for good results.

WARNING: It can do NSFW imgs.

This version come with my style lora in it. You will get a lot of similar face outputs. You can get the model with out my style at LibraMix.

All preview images are generated with below settings:

  • VAE: [kl-f8-anime2]

  • Clip Skip: 2

  • Sampling method: SDE Karras

  • Sampling steps: 30

  • Hires.fix: on

  • Upscaler: Remacri Upscaler

  • Hires steps: 10-12

  • Denoising strength: (0.4 - 0.5)

  • Upscale by: 2

  • WxH: 512x768

  • CFG Scale: 5 (5 - 7.5)

Check preview for negative prompt and embedding that I may use.
